{"type": "article", "id": 31598, "title": "连绵的木头雪山上，挂什么都可以｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2016-08-29T23:03:49Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 32139, "name": "rutan Studio"}, {"id": 32140, "name": "Brave Space Design"}, {"id": 32141, "name": "Leaf & Clay"}, {"id": 32142, "name": "By Lassen"}, {"id": 32143, "name": "Elena Prokhorova"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 95, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160829233853SxkOmgNGEK7YHV1D.jpg", "contents": "<p class=\"\">          </p><p>          </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Horatio lampshade by rutan Studio</h3><p>德国设计工作室 <a href=\"http://rutan.de/home\" rel=\"nofollow\">rutan Studio</a> 最近与日本的 <a href=\"http://www.aporo-ss.co.jp/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Aporo 制作公司</a>利用独创的印刷工艺联手打造了一款有着飘逸感的灯具 Horatio。灯罩在挂起后会像布料一样自然垂落下来，光线映照出表面通过丝印技术打造的叶脉一样的纹路，带给人一种独特的照明体验。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.shushu-online.de/advanced_search_result.php?categories_id=0&amp;keywords=horatio&amp;inc_subcat=1\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 149 欧元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160829234255wloWYES3AaM1ZrXt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.618582\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160829234255Bz8MKxP9QEidsgFa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.557457\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608292342551JOhYupfV4MS8sdb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.611247\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160829234255d5gAzFERZlWOKhsq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.611247\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160829234255rax5PFLcWCsY4Ifu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.611247\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608292342557lHESris63LzvQq9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.297066\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Spiky by Elena Prokhorova</h3><p>这张名为 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/42034551/SPIKY-desk\" rel=\"nofollow\">Spiky</a> 的概念书桌是乌克兰设计师 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/elena_prokhorova\" rel=\"nofollow\">Elena Prokhorova</a> 的最新作品：书桌采用两层结构，在木制桌面和它下方的黑色台面间有一个多功能的储物空间。这个夹层的正中央是一个平整的倒梯形，但 Prokhorova 并没有在两侧将这种规整的风格延续下去，而是将台面设计成起伏不平的造型，可以用来分门别类地放置一些小物。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160829234238pJsHSe2W30KQ59jE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160829234237xSs4knELhped3rmX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160829234237sug3rYlAZWjzUVcF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160829234237aChJdcbYulnSZKq0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160829234236sgINnHrCBKYv63yd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>My Own Chair by By Lassen</h3><p>在即将举行的巴黎时尚家居设计展秋展上，丹麦设计品牌 <a href=\"http://bylassen.com/shop/frontpage.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">By Lassen</a> 除了展示自己的秋冬新款之外，还将带来由设计师 Flemming Lassen 在 1938 年设计的经典扶手椅 My Own Chair。它如翼的椅背看上去非常优雅，支在木制支架上同下方的座椅分开了一段距离，这样的设计在当时的现代主义者眼中都过于超前。By Lassen 推出了三种全新的款式，有织物和皮革两种材质可选。这是它的<a href=\"http://bylassen.com/shop/my-own-chair-96c1.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 3199 到 6299 欧元不等。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608292342160pd3lcaKZOrAJQ2N.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.713867\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160829234215jrEgOdTxcPH4vzsn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.713867\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160829234215oGXQD2pYqgH4arwE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.713867\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160829234215b5lALdn4hOseRDi7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.713867\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160829234216GWZdQsBibL7tnIoM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.713867\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608292342168Tvbu3JmzX4jpVCn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.713867\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Coat Range by Brave Space Design</h3><p>由 Kragiel 设计师夫妇于 2005 年创立的 <a href=\"http://www.bravespacedesign.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Brave Space Design</a> 是一间专精于木制家具的工作室，最近他们就以派拉蒙影业标志上壮观的大提顿山为灵感设计了一款山脉形的衣架。Coat Range 由深色的胡桃木和作为雪峰的浅色枫木组成，在墙面上排成一排就能够打造出连绵不绝的木制山脉，使人眼前一亮。这是它的<a href=\"http://www.bravespacedesign.com/shop/coat-range\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 195 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160829234155w8T4qrMtPj9lAu0X.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160829234155GtuKzE4B0yW2SiTH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160829234155tNFulXL32CrJ0miz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160829234155HQdrMSJzCks1qget.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Leaf &amp; Clay pot by Leaf &amp; Clay</h3><p>凭着对多肉植物以及手工制品的喜爱，来自加州的 Sandford 兄妹成立了一个名为 <a href=\"http://leafandclay.co/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Leaf &amp; Clay</a> 的博客，为了让同好们能够以更好看的方式呈现自己心爱的多肉植物，他们与印尼的五位工匠联手打造了一套与博客同名的多肉植物盆。Leaf &amp; Clay 系列一共有六种不同的款式，所有花盆都在印尼由工匠利用当地的丰饶的火山土手工打造。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/363741693/leaf-and-clay-handcrafted-succulent-pots\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，最低价为 40 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160829234137qkoBKsdvDczJlZnY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160829234137eQNLEhA2w80vJSk5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608292341385M3Q6qYL0Kun87Jr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.827004\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160829234137ZEFAKwT4JxhgjnMI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664179\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160829234137Zmg3QBzAebsdrxn9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666170\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608292341374mu7pcYXtJjQqNxl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.663205\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>FLAVTISS by Saya Edwin</h3><p>这个名为 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/41742509/FLAVTISS\" rel=\"nofollow\">FLAVTISS</a> 的概念纸巾品牌是印尼设计学生 <a href=\"http://edwin.id/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Saya Edwin</a> 的作品，所代表的香型通过包装的颜色和可爱的水果直观地呈现给顾客。三角形的纸盒不需要胶水的帮助就可以直接折叠起来，左右两端组合在一起刚好能够拼成一个水果图案。为了吸引更多人的注意力，Edwin 还设计了一个配套的展示板，中间的纸盒彼此相连就像是一个三色的阶梯。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160829234103kOH1pQKoGCtzTUPl.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608292341051XoNsObEC4pA807S.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666429\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160829234106GSYkqAPQIr8hl9TD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.735714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160829234106o4tfzRM27P5DgarA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.607143\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608292341050xHEThsd1BgUJrNe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.071429\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160829234105wU5nN1uYmKCIHyL7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.071429\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}